years senior to_me by chance in the mid-sixties came across waterfall behind the house reprinted in some journal completely distant in my conundrum it was short story originally published in an_anthology of his works moonlight in spring night it was very impressive for its_visionary and_flowing impetus completely different from the physiognomy that met before the second phase of_the tet offensive 1968 thác đổ truyện_ngắn bối-cảnh hoang-zã thác-đổ sau-nhà jống chén rượu ngọt-ngào_ngây-ngất thiên-nhiên ru fụ-nữ hồn-nhiên jấc-ngủ mơn-trớn ngón tuyệt-xảo thân-thể con_người đàn ngón êm_ái fụ-nữ fải ngưòi đàn-bà quyến-rũ gi tác-fẩm water fall behind the_house short story 1956 the wilderness background offers some shots of_intoxicating nectar of_nature enough to lull_a care free woman into wonderful sleep that soon turned into a_dream by dexterity if human body were an_instrument then his fingers like spring breeze nurtured desire for her innocence that dream only returned amidst boisterous laughers in one evening party for the seductive voice to_resurrect that voice which once came forward her_unceremoniously and_magically caressed hidden desire to her heavenly climatic instinct of human nature would she have been led on the reader has no certainty but only continued to read beyond fine letters nguyên-vẹn tiểu-thuyết 1978 nguyên-vẹn võ-phiến hai í-ngĩa tinh-tuý uyên-nguyên tình-iêu mong-manh tình-iêu tan-vỡ tự-nhiên con-người vận-hội ham-muốn bất-ngờ zo ước_mong tình-iêu nguyên-vẹn không_tưởng zi-tản việt năm_bảy lăm_trưng lắm rối_mù hi-vọng vong-thân novel content to represent_võ-phiến play of double meanings the pristine or original state of_love and_the uncertainty for love is breakable because it is human that no one can resist_opportunity and_temptation and that raises the question of_securing harmony both_crystal-like and ephemeral impossible the 1975 vietnamese diaspora exposed the test of survival_instinct and_the traditional culture of_value using contradictory mosaic images of_hope as well as of_alienation of_unity as well as separation in such dramatic destiny there came a_young woman named zung dung in looking for her boy friend in any point of_space and_time breathlessly_expanding and contracting psychologically in such leeway of her uncertainty ridiculous encounters led in such as the case of_triêm family_man in his middle-age a_fine devoutee of_buddhist teaching practice daily only at night he turned wildly in bed with his wife who was amazed but did not realize that her husband was penetrating other women in fantasy it is wonderful exposition of_psychiatry diagnose without knowing freudian dream interpretations that prompted me to publish note in the book review section of_viêtnam culture journal
